\n<br />\n想問下3個月大係咪就咁食普通貓糧就得?<br />\n<br />\n定要攪碎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34967a9d331cd1f6bd9f8d9b58da181f36857206","tid":291013,"uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c02efe626d2cfe775a3ef2eba1dae6b8b1d546","tid":291013,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好等貓媽媽教識佢去廁所呀，生活習慣個啲先<br />\n準備都係窗網貓砂盆個啲野，有心既上網search下邊隻糧對貓bb好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗2個月大應該可以接番去啦，<br />\n不過個時接我主人係等到佢差不多3個月大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有清潔下自己屋企，一啲窿，sofa底，<br />\n貓貓一開頭驚/有時玩會匿埋，如果太多塵會鼻塞<br />\n利申主人有鼻敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日鼻塞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝絲打分享<br />\n<br />\n我遲啲會清潔屋企啲位架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下3個月大係咪就咁食普通貓糧就得?<br />\n<br />\n定要攪碎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通糧就ok<br />\n灑d貓奶粉or營養補充粉囉"},{"pid":"2960f974a508db1f2a16e5d3c12e68fc9d4db3e2","tid":291013,"uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}